WEBVTT

00:07:00.234 --> 00:07:03.111
We're weighing the merits
of two jobs, after all,

00:07:03.135 --> 00:07:06.268
not the merits of the number nine
and a plate of fried eggs.

00:07:08.052 --> 00:07:11.396
A comparison of the overall
merits of two jobs

00:07:11.420 --> 00:07:13.307
is something we can make,

00:07:13.331 --> 00:07:15.468
and one we often do make.

00:07:17.407 --> 00:07:19.463
I think the puzzle arises

00:07:19.487 --> 00:07:23.265
because of an unreflective assumption
we make about value.

